quran[3]{c,v,t,f}:
  2,16,"Àwọn wọ̀nyẹn ni àwọn tí wọ́n fi ìmọ̀nà ra ìṣìnà.{1} Nítorí náà, òkòwò wọn kò lérè, wọn kò sì jẹ́ olùmọ̀nà..",1:[Ọmọ ‘Abbās - kí Allāhu yọ́nú sí àwọn méjèèjì - sọ pé, “Wọ́n mú ìṣìnà, wọ́n sì fi ìmọ̀nà sílẹ̀.” Tafsīr bun Kathīr.]
  2,17,"Àpèjúwe wọn dà bí àpèjúwe ẹni tí ó tan iná, ṣùgbọ́n nígbà tí ìmọ́lẹ̀ tàn sí àyíká rẹ̀ tán, Allāhu mú ìmọ́lẹ̀ wọn lọ, Ó sì fi wọ́n sílẹ̀ sínú àwọn òkùnkùn; wọn kò sì ríran mọ́."
  2,18,"Adití, ayaya, afọ́jú ni wọ́n; nítorí náà wọn kò níí ṣẹ́rí padà."